Grafida 0.2
================================================================================
# [HIGH] Windows: the app crashed immediately on startup ("broken signature") because Authenticode signing corrupted the Boson-appended PHAR payload
# [MEDIUM] Windows: the interface froze for several seconds whenever a stored secret was read, because the secret store spawned PowerShell; it now uses the DPAPI system call directly
# [LOW] Windows: a command window no longer flashes (at startup, and when detecting the system light/dark theme)
+ Windows: the installer now bundles the required Visual C++ runtime DLLs, so the app runs on a clean Windows without a separate redistributable
+ The editor now shows the article alias (URL slug) below the title, auto-generated from the title using Joomla's conventions, with a button to regenerate it
+ Ctrl/Cmd+, now opens the Settings page from anywhere (prompting to save first when an article is open with unsaved changes)

Grafida 0.1
================================================================================
+ First release
+ Connect to one or more Joomla! 5.4+ sites through the Web Services (REST) API
+ Browse, search, sort, filter and paginate a site's articles, mirroring the Joomla back-end list
+ Create and edit articles in a TinyMCE 7 WYSIWYG editor with the site's own editor.css
+ Local article drafts stored offline in SQLite; edit a remote article as an unsaved draft
+ Offline media picker, inline image handling and a full online Media Manager screen
+ Publish articles back to the site (intro/full-text split, categories, tags, custom fields, images)
+ AI chat assistant and writing tools (multiple configurable providers; streaming replies)
+ Inserting an AI reply into the editor converts Markdown to HTML and preserves class/style formatting
+ Markdown import, light/dark/auto interface theme, and seven interface languages
+ Native desktop application for macOS, Windows and Linux built with Boson
